      "para_id": "Q000905.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Nindara , the mighty master , his master , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of the E-sirara , Nanše's temple , dedicated this ( mace ) for his well-being ."
